    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior retains a strong shine, though you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and very light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car is sound, shifts smoothly, and has a complete service history. It is a reliable, attractive option for someone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle that needs no immediate repairs.",
