    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is ready for its next chapter and offers a fantastic opportunity for someone who loves to roll up their sleeves. While it shows significant wear and will require some dedicated mechanical attention and TLC to get back to its best, it\u2019s a budget-friendly entry point for a rewarding restoration project!",
